name: Go! Green boy Go!
description:
I created this game to begin learning game development. It's short and only has a couple of different mechanics. I would like to expand on it with more levels, and mechanics, and add a story eventually, but I'm first going to try to create some more short games to expand my abilities in Unreal Engine 5. 

The goal is to reach the diamond within 1 minute. Thank you for playing! Please let me know if you encounter any bugs.
